msgstr "Stel de hoofdmap in om te zoeken naar kdoctools."

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--param</option> key=value"
msgstr "<option>--param</option> key=waarde"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set parameters to pass to the stylesheet."
msgstr "Stel parameters in om door te geven aan het stijlblad."

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Gebruik"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common way to run <command>meinproc6</command> is simply as "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
"index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. Note "
"that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
"&konqueror;)."
msgstr ""
"De meest gewone manier om <command>meinproc6</command> uit te voeren is "
"gewoon als <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-bestand</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> waar <replaceable>docbook-bestand</replaceable> meestal "
"index.docbook is. Dit commando maakt &HTML;-pagina's aan uit het DocBook-"
"bestand. Opmerking: deze pagina's zijn alleen in te zien in de op &kde; "
"gebaseerde browsers (zoals &konqueror;)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
"you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
"full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
"produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
"<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgstr ""
"Als u de &HTML;-uitvoer in een andere browser wilt zien (bijvoorbeeld, als u "
"het online zet), gebruik dan <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"naam</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-bestand</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> waar <replaceable>stylesheet-naam</replaceable> het "
"volledige pad is naar een van de &XSL;-stijlbladen in &lt;"
"kdoctools_installatie_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. Om "
"uitvoer te maken dat geschikt is voor het web, kunt u het commando "
"<command>kde-web.xsl</command> of <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command> "
"gebruiken. Zie het bestand <filename>README</filename> in die map voor meer "
"details."

